Device: Kindle DX, Yotaphone 2, iPhone7+, Dasung 13.3" HD-FT Monitor, iPad Pro**First in-depth review of Onyx Mira 13.3" monitor**

* * *

 Been searching YouTube for months ... awaiting to see if this will be a worthwhile product. I am not associated with the reviewer, but do watch his vids and he always gives a thorough testing/review of the Pros & Cons:

[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xFEiqJzi32U](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xFEiqJzi32U)

 I already have a Dasung 13.3" HD-FT monitor, but I do need something bigger for my computer needs ... and the 25.3" Mira Pro is to be released "soon", so I'm going to keep an eye out for it ... although the price tag for the Mira Pro is going to be way too much!
